courses.learning_outcomes:
After completing this course, students should be able to:
1. describe and examine topics related to university education, university life, history and tradition of Chung Chi College;
2. recognize contemporary and perennial issues covered in GEJC1120;
3. develop effective communication and critical thinking skills;
4. demonstrate the ability to work in team.

修讀本科後，同學將能夠：
1. 闡述及探討有關大學教育及大學生活的題目，以及崇基學院歷史與傳統；
2. 理解GEJC1120講課中當今與恆常的課題；
3. 培養有效溝通能力和批判思考；
4. 展示團隊合作能力。
